<h1 id="start-server">Start Server</h1>

<p>‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏™‡∏¥‡πà‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏Å‡πá‡∏°‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏ñ‡∏≠‡∏∞ ‡πÇ‡∏î‡∏¢‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏ù‡∏±‡πà‡∏á Server ‡∏Å‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏ô‡∏∞‡∏à‡πä‡∏∞</p>

<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>    <span class="nx">mkdir</span> <span class="nx">ionic</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="nx">chat</span>
    <span class="nx">cd</span> <span class="nx">ionic</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="nx">chat</span>
    <span class="nx">npm</span> <span class="nx">init</span>
    <span class="nx">npm</span> <span class="nx">install</span> <span class="nx">socket</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">io</span> <span class="nx">express</span> <span class="o">--</span><span class="nx">save</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>socket.io ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏™‡πà‡∏á‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö real time ‡∏™‡πà‡∏ß‡∏ô express ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô server (‡∏à‡∏£‡∏¥‡∏á‡πÜ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏Å‡πá‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÅ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏ú‡∏°‡∏Ç‡∏µ‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏Å‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏à‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏≠‡πà‡∏∞‡∏°‡∏µ‡πÑ‡∏£‡∏õ‡πà‡∏∞) ‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ó‡∏≥‡πÄ‡∏™‡∏£‡πá‡∏à‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå index.js ‡∏Ç‡∏∂‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏≤‡πÇ‡∏î‡∏¢‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà Code ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏•‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏•‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏õ
<b>index.js</b></p>

<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">express</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">require</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">express</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">app</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">express</span><span class="p">();</span>
<span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">server</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">require</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">http</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="nx">createServer</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">app</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">io</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">require</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">socket.io</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="nx">listen</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">server</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="nx">app</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">use</span><span class="p">((</span><span class="nx">req</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">res</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">next</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="nx">res</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">header</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">Access-Control-Allow-Origin</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">*</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">);</span>
    <span class="nx">res</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">header</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">Access-Control-Allow-Headers</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">Origin, X-Requested-With, Content-Type, Accept</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">);</span>
    <span class="nx">next</span><span class="p">();</span>
<span class="p">});</span>
<span class="nx">app</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="kd">get</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">/</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">req</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">res</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span><span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="nx">res</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">send</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">This is ma awesome server</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="p">});</span>
<span class="nx">io</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">on</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">connection</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">client</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="nx">console</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">log</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">Client connected...</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">);</span>
    <span class="nx">client</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">on</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">msg</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">message</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
        <span class="nx">io</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">emit</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">msg</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">message</span><span class="p">);</span>
    <span class="p">});</span>
<span class="p">});</span>
<span class="nx">server</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">listen</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">5555</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">()</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="nx">console</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">log</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">Program running on port : 5555</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="p">});</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>‡πÅ‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏∞‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ù‡∏±‡πà‡∏á Server ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ö‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏≠‡∏ò‡∏¥‡∏ö‡∏≤‡∏¢ Code ‡∏ô‡∏∞‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö</p>

<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">express</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">require</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">express</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">app</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">express</span><span class="p">();</span>
<span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">server</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">require</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">http</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="nx">createServer</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">app</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">io</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">require</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">socket.io</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="nx">listen</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">server</span><span class="p">);</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏Å‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á server ‡πÇ‡∏î‡∏¢‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ express ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏ú‡∏π‡∏Å Socket.io ‡πÑ‡∏ß‡πâ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö server ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ñ‡∏π‡∏Å‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏Ç‡∏∂‡πâ‡∏ô</p>
<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nx">app</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">use</span><span class="p">((</span><span class="nx">req</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">res</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">next</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="nx">res</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">header</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">Access-Control-Allow-Origin</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">);</span>
    <span class="nx">res</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">header</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">Access-Control-Allow-Headers</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">Origin, X-Requested-With, Content-Type, Accept</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">);</span>
    <span class="nx">next</span><span class="p">();</span>
<span class="p">});</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>‡πÄ‡∏ã‡πá‡∏ó Header ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏Å‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å server ‡∏≠‡∏∑‡πà‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ</p>
<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nx">app</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="kd">get</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">/</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">req</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">res</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span><span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="nx">res</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">send</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">This is ma awesome server</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="p">});</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>‡πÄ‡∏ã‡πá‡∏ó route ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏≤‡πÉ‡∏ô server ‡∏ú‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏≤‡∏á browser</p>
<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nx">io</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">on</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">connection</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">client</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
  <span class="p">...</span>
<span class="p">});</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô event ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏Å‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏Ç‡∏∂‡πâ‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏≤‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏ó‡πà‡∏≠</p>
<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nx">client</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">on</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">msg</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">message</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
  <span class="p">...</span>
<span class="p">});</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô event ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏Å‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏Ç‡∏∂‡πâ‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏™‡πà‡∏á‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏ú‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏ó‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤ msg</p>
<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nx">io</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">emit</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">msg</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">message</span><span class="p">);</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>‡∏™‡πà‡∏á msg ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏Ñ‡∏ô</p>
<blockquote>
‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏´‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏™‡πà‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏Ñ‡∏ô‡∏¢‡∏Å‡πÄ‡∏ß‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏Ñ‡∏ô‡∏™‡πà‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô

```js
client.broadcast.emit('msg', message);
```

‡πÅ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏™‡πà‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏•‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏õ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏Ñ‡∏ô‡∏™‡πà‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß‡πÄ‡∏ó‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô(‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤ chat ‡πÑ‡∏´‡∏°‡∏´‡∏ô‡∏≠) ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô

```js
client.emit('msg', message);
```

</blockquote>

<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nx">server</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">listen</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">5555</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">()</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="nx">console</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">log</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">Program running on port : 5555</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="p">});</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á server ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà port 5555 ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏¢‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á</p>
