</code></pre></div></div>
<p>‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å Code ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ö‡∏ô‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏à‡∏∏‡∏î‡∏™‡∏±‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏Å‡∏ï‡∏∏ 3 ‡∏à‡∏∏‡∏î‡∏î‡∏±‡∏á‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ</p>
<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nt">&lt;ion-card</span> <span class="na">*ngFor=</span><span class="s">"let msg of massage"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;ion-card-content&gt;</span>
      {{ msg }}
    <span class="nt">&lt;/ion-card-content&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/ion-card&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>*ngFor=‚Äù‚Ä¶‚Äù ‡∏Ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏ô‡∏•‡∏π‡∏õ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á Angular2 ‡∏™‡πà‡∏ß‡∏ô {{ msg }} ‡∏Ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤ Object ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á Angular2 ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤ Two-way binding (‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏ß‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏ò‡∏¥‡∏ö‡∏≤‡∏¢‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏ö‡∏ó‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡πÜ‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏ô‡∏∞‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö) ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏™‡πà‡∏ß‡∏ô‡∏™‡∏∏‡∏î‡∏ó‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏¢ (click)=‚Äùsend()‚Äù ‡∏Ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏° event click ‡∏ô‡∏∞‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô Javascript ‡∏ò‡∏£‡∏£‡∏°‡∏î‡∏≤‡∏Å‡πá‡∏≠‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏°‡∏ì‡πå Onclick ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏ì‡∏ô‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô
‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏ô‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ó‡∏î‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏¢‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á &lt;pre&gt;ionic serve&lt;/pre&gt; ionic ‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î Browser ‡∏Ç‡∏∂‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏≤‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ï‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏•‡πà‡∏≤‡πÜ ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏ì‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏∞‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö
<img src="/img/ionic-chat/img02.png" alt="‡∏ó‡∏î‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏≠‡∏û" />
<span class="caption text-muted">‡∏ó‡∏î‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏≠‡∏û‡∏ú‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô Browser</span>
‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏≤‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå Page/home/home.ts ‡∏Ç‡∏∂‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏≤‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÅ‡∏Å‡πâ‡πÑ‡∏Ç‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡∏î‡∏±‡∏á‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏∞‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö</p>
<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">import</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="nx">Component</span> <span class="p">}</span> <span class="k">from</span> <span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">@angular/core</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">;</span>

<span class="k">import</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="nx">NavController</span> <span class="p">}</span> <span class="k">from</span> <span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">ionic-angular</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">;</span>

<span class="nx">declare</span> <span class="kd">var</span> <span class="nx">io</span><span class="p">;</span>

<span class="p">@</span><span class="nd">Component</span><span class="p">({</span>
  <span class="na">selector</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">page-home</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span>
  <span class="na">templateUrl</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">home.html</span><span class="dl">'</span>
<span class="p">})</span>
<span class="k">export</span> <span class="kd">class</span> <span class="nx">HomePage</span> <span class="p">{</span>

  <span class="nl">socketHost</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">string</span><span class="p">;</span>
  <span class="nl">socket</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">any</span><span class="p">;</span>
  <span class="nl">massage</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">any</span><span class="p">;</span>
  <span class="nl">msg</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">string</span><span class="p">;</span>
  <span class="kd">constructor</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kr">public</span> <span class="nx">navCtrl</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">NavController</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="k">this</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">socketHost</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">http://localhost:5555</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="k">this</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">massage</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[];</span>
    <span class="k">this</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">socket</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">io</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">this</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">socketHost</span><span class="p">);</span>
    <span class="k">this</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">socket</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">on</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">msg</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">msg</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
      <span class="k">this</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">massage</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">push</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">msg</span><span class="p">);</span>
    <span class="p">});</span>
  <span class="p">}</span>

  <span class="nx">send</span><span class="p">(){</span>
    <span class="k">this</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">socket</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">emit</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">msg</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="k">this</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">msg</span><span class="p">);</span>
    <span class="k">this</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">msg</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="dl">""</span><span class="p">;</span>
  <span class="p">}</span>

<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>‡∏≠‡∏ò‡∏¥‡∏ö‡∏≤‡∏¢ Code ‡∏ô‡∏∞‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö</p>
<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nx">declare</span> <span class="kd">var</span> <span class="nx">io</span><span class="p">;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>‡∏Ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏®‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡πÅ‡∏õ‡∏£ io ‡∏ô‡∏∞‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏à‡∏£‡∏¥‡∏á‡πÜ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏®‡∏Å‡πá‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÅ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß Typescript ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏£‡∏π‡πâ‡∏à‡∏±‡∏Å io ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏®‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏á‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏á‡∏≠‡πÅ‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏≤</p>
<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>  <span class="nx">socketHost</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">string</span><span class="p">;</span>
  <span class="nl">socket</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nl">any</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">any</span><span class="p">;</span>
  <span class="nl">massage</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">string</span><span class="p">[];</span>
  <span class="nl">msg</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">string</span><span class="p">;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏®‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡πÅ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÜ ‡∏ô‡∏∞‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö</p>
<ul>
<li>socketHost ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô string ‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö url ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á server</li>
<li>socket ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö socket ‡∏ô‡∏∞‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏£‡∏π‡πâ‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ type ‡∏≠‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô any (any ‡∏Ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ó‡πà‡∏≤‡πÑ‡∏°‡πâ‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏Ñ‡∏¥‡∏î type ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏Å any ‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏Å‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô 555)</li>
<li>massage ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà chat ‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏°‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô string array</li>
<li>msg ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏ä‡πà‡∏≠‡∏á input ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô string</li>
</ul>
<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">this</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">socketHost</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">http://localhost:5555</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="k">this</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">massage</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[];</span>
